ïóŸRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2024-03-30-twin0240.mdŸ@bc1c4f8a364beaa55b58686a57d3ae7f216565e6222da0f3e7b4aae629bbfe7cπThis week in Nushell #240ëßNushell⁄åsholderbach made a ton of changes: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12335] reused existing small allocations where possible
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12334] used nightly clippy for dead code removal/style fixes
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12325] elided a clone in 
``V::follow_cell_path``
 for record
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12312] avoided uses of 
``Record``
 internals again
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12310] fixed a bug with history hints and case sensitivity
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12309] renamed 
``Value::CustomValue``
 to 
``Value::Custom``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12307] deduplicated 
``nix``
 dependency versions
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12293] benchmarked table creation and access
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12292] fixed 
``return``
 in 
``filter``
 closure eval
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12285] moved some 
``Option``
 if/else to method chains in style
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12284] removed dead 
``impl PluginEncoder for EncodingType``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12283] followed API guidelines for public types
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12333] introduced a 
``--guess flag``
 and removed 
``--legacy``
 for 
``detect columns``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12277] improved the default algorithm in 
``detect columns``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12232] made 
``ls``
, 
``rm``
, 
``cp``
, 
``open``
, 
``touch``
, 
``mkdir``
 not expand tilde if input path is a quoted string or a variable
dead10ck 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12328] fixed insertion of null values in 
``into sqlite``
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12323] fixed the build of nu-protocol without the plugin feature enabled
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12319] removed serde derive for 
``ShellError``
, replaced via 
``LabeledError``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12282] replaced the 
``difference``
 crate with 
``similar``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12281] added example tests (nu-plugin-test-support) for plugins in repo
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12279] changed PluginCommand API to be more like Command
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12321] fixed file redirection for external streams
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12317] made 
``Record.cols``
 private
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12315] used safe 
``nix``
 APIs instead of 
``libc``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12298] cancelled old CI runs on commit
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12294] always pretty printed binary values in 
``table``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12291] added a 
``command_prelude``
 module
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12316] added a few more logging statements for debugging startup
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12311] kept sqlparser at 39 until polars is upgraded
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12286] cleaned up coreutils tagging
merelymyself 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12308] exposed the recursion limit value as a config option
AucaCoyan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12306] reworked some help strings
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12273] fixed a bug with IDE tooltips
FilipAndersson245 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12297] fixed a broken benchmark
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12252] boxed records for smaller Value enum
Dorumin 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12249] implemented parameterization for 
``query db``
dmatos2012 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11684] created an initial implementation for uutils 
``uname``
schrieveslaach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11443] included more info for LSP completion
